<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-07-0725 </DOCNO><TEXT>This suggestion contains the following topics: present situation; obstacles,economic aspects and other factors in connection with the further developmentof renewable energy sources, sectoral analyses (solar energy, biomass,geothermal energy, wind energy, hydraulic power). In conclusion, a suggestionfor a recommendation of the Council to the Member States on the furtherdevelopment of the use of renewable energy sources is described.</TEXT></DOC>